comment: Hello from India. I am very grateful to you, I can say that you are my motivation to start again something new in my life. I was very depressed for 2 years, my father passed away. I couldn’t able to acknowledge it. He was there for me when I needed him the most, After marriage also I was depended on him mentally. He helped me to gain confidence in my education and career. He was my hero. I am too shy in front of people, don’t know why. I have low confidence, so I didn’t know how to regain my confidence back. One day I found your channel and started watching it. I started liking you, the way you prepare food, your living style, etc..  Your videos calms me. Even though I am a vegetarian I love your cooking. Then one day I got an Idea & started filming my daily life routine. I never uploaded it until my husband encouraged me a lot to upload it & create my channel. I am too shy to show my face, but thanks to you I am getting my confidence back. Lots of love and thanks.
